on><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 00:26:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/joscha-bach-galactic-game-theory</guid></item><item><title>为什么你应该质疑遗传风险评分</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/why-you-should-question-genetic-risk-scores</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 00:11:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/why-you-should-question-genetic-risk-scores</guid></item><item><title>麻省理工学院的研究人员发现，三种麻醉药物对大脑都有相同的作用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/three-anesthesia-drugs-all-have-the-same-effect-in-the-brain-mit-researchers-find</link><description>当患者接受全身麻醉时，医生可以在多种药物中进行选择。尽管这些药物以不同的方式作用于神经元，但它们都会导致相同的结果：根据麻省理工学院的一项新研究，破坏大脑稳定性和兴奋性之间的平衡。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/three-anesthesia-drugs-all-have-the-same-effect-in-the-brain-mit-researchers-find.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 23:56:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/three-anesthesia-drugs-all-have-the-same-effect-in-the-brain-mit-researchers-find</guid></item><item><title>克劳德代码的秘密生活：阅读你没有写的代码</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-secret-life-of-claude-code-reading-code-you-didnt-write</link><description>如何在陌生的代码库中定位自己 - 以及 Claude Code 如何帮助您在不失去判断力的情况下找到立足点。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-secret-life-of-claude-code-reading-code-you-didnt-write.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 23:41:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-secret-life-of-claude-code-reading-code-you-didnt-write</guid></item><item><title>科学家称地球上有一片海洋不接触陆地，那是因为它没有海岸</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-say-there-is-one-sea-on-earth-that-touches-no-land-and-that-is-because-it-has-no-shore</link><description>大西洋拥有一个秘密：一片平静的水域，周围环绕着急流，位于佛罗里达州以东约 590 英里处，但从未接触过陆地。数百年来，水手们一直在被称为马尾藻海的地方穿越它，但当他们滑入玻璃般的靛蓝色海水时，很少有人注意到边界。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-say-there-is-one-sea-on-earth-that-touches-no-land-and-that-is-because-it-has-no-shore2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 23:26:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-say-there-is-one-sea-on-earth-that-touches-no-land-and-that-is-because-it-has-no-shore</guid></item><item><title>科学家创造出第一个能够与人脑交流的人工神经元</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-create-the-first-artificial-neuron-capable-of-communicating-with-the-human-brain</link><description>科学家们创造了一种人工神经元，它的工作电压与活细胞相同，并且能够与人脑进行交流。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-create-the-first-artificial-neuron-capable-of-communicating-with-the-human-brain.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 23:11:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-create-the-first-artificial-neuron-capable-of-communicating-with-the-human-brain</guid></item><item><title>大脑功能的通用理论</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-universal-theory-of-brain-function</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 22:56:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-universal-theory-of-brain-function</guid></item></channel></rss>